Your Journey, Our Compassion

 Rediscover Yourself in the Heart of Bali

Welcome to Satu Nusa Addiction Treatment and Mental Health, where true change begins. We are more than just a typical rehabilitation center; we are your destination for a healthier and happier life. Located on Serangan Island, South Denpasar, Bali, Indonesia, we blend the island’s serene natural beauty and rich local culture with our signature Satu Nusa Holistic Therapy®

 

What Makes Us Different?

We recognize that each recovery journey is unique. That is why we provide Satu Nusa Holistic Therapy®, a program designed to emphasize mindset and behavioral transformation in order to achieve the Eight Pillars of Holistic Well-being, addressing both addiction and mental health challenges.

Satu Nusa Rehabilitation : Your Path to Recovery

Satu Nusa, from the Sanskrit for “One Island,” embodies the spirit of unity and belonging. As a recovery house established in Denpasar on September 12, 2022, we are dedicated to providing compassionate care for all forms of addiction and mental health issues, free from discrimination based on tribe, religion, race, or group.

Legal and Professional 

Satu Nusa operates with full legal legitimacy, holding a Notary Deed (No. 52) and a decree from the Minister of Law and Human Rights (No. AHU-0018979). We are also a proud partner of the Bali Province National Narcotics Agency (No. PKS/11/IV/KA/HK.02/2024). Our proven recovery treatment method is officially registered with the Directorate General of Intellectual Property Rights (No. 000563815).

Exclusive and Personalized Care

 As an exclusive recovery house committed to privacy, we accept a maximum of three clients at a time. Our facilities include comfortable single and twin rooms, each with air conditioning. We provide one dedicated counselor per client, ensuring focused and personalized support throughout your journey.

A Serene Environment

 Satu Nusa is located on Serangan Island, offering a peaceful setting for recovery. Our location provides easy access to local landmarks like Sakenan Temple, the Turtle Conservation and Education Center, Serangan Beach, and Serangan Harbor, allowing you to find peace and tranquility.

 

Vision

To be a leading recovery house dedicated to helping individuals overcome addiction and mental health challenges, empowering them to live productive lives through our Satu Nusa Holistic Therapy®.

Mission

Our mission is to guide clients toward holistic well-being by focusing on eight core pillars:

Emotional Well-being: Developing skills to understand and manage personal emotions.

Spiritual Well-being: Fostering a search for purpose and meaning in life.

Intellectual Well-being: Promoting mental growth through stimulating activities.

Physical Well-being: Encouraging a healthy lifestyle for optimal physical health.

Environmental Well-being: Harmonizing physical and mental activities with nature and local wisdom.

Financial Well-being: Building a supportive foundation for financial stability.

Occupational Well-being: Cultivating satisfaction and purpose in one’s work.

Social Well-being: Nurturing healthy social interactions and relationships.
